panels.description:
The number of completed verification jobs and their results. 
- error means the job failed and has to be retried
- invalid means an expected replica did not exist
- valid means the expected replica existed
panels.title: Completed Verification Jobs by Result

panels.description: The number of leases that had to be released due to the verification worker not expectedly releasing the lease on job completion.
panels.title: Stale Verification Leases Released

panels.description: Number of repositories that don't have any up to date replicas available.
panels.title: Unavailable Repositories

panels.description: Latency that Praefect adds to RPCs

panels.title: Praefect Added Latency
